description:
If even the most Left Wing Newspaper in the world @guardian has doubts about @danielandrewsmp plan to obtain from parliament an extension of the State of Emergency powers, well, that means Dan has really crossed the line!
I remind you Dan that the reason the S.O.E. has been created with a 6 months time limit is because politician like You WONT ABUSE IT the way You are doing now.
I appeal to the Victorian Parliament and in particular to crossbenchers and labour MP who still believe in a #Democracy :
If you vote in favour, not only you will be an accomplice in destroying more lives and businesses but you will create a VERY DANGEROUS PRECEDENT for every future Premier to abuse of those extreme powers that are now limited.
Don't forget also US people of Melbourne and Victoria, we won't just sit and watch our Great State become a #Socialist #dictatorship .

 #pandemic #plandemic2020 #covidscam #covid #covid19 #virus #freedom #nofacemask  #wakeupaustralia #Melbourne #Victoria #Australia #fakenews
#sackdanielandrews #dictatorship #idonotconsent #nojabnopay
